quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  16,124,"Àwọn tí wọ́n ṣe (àgbéga) ọjọ́ Sabt fún ni àwọn tó yapa-ẹnu lórí rẹ̀.{1} Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ yóò kúkú ṣe ìdájọ́ láààrin wọn ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń yapa-ẹnu lórí rẹ̀..",footnotes:1:[Yíyapa-ẹnu tí àwọn yẹhudi yapa-ẹnu lórí ṣíṣe àgbéga fún ọjọ́ Jímọ̀, tí wọ́n sì fi ọjọ́ Sabt dípò rẹ̀, l’ó ṣokùnfà bí ọjọ́ náà ṣe di dandan fún ọ̀wọ́ wọn nìkan láti ṣe àgbéga rẹ̀.]
  16,125,"Pèpè sí ojú ọ̀nà Olúwa rẹ pẹ̀lú ọgbọ́n ìjìnlẹ̀ (ìyẹn, al-Ƙur’ān àti sunnah Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -) àti wáàsí rere. Kí o sì jà wọ́n níyàn pẹ̀lú èyí tó dára jùlọ. Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun l’Ó nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tí ó ṣìnà kúrò lójú ọ̀nà Rẹ̀ (’Islām). Òun l’Ó sì nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa àwọn olùmọ̀nà (àwọn mùsùlùmí)."
  16,126,"Tí ẹ (bá fẹ́) gbẹ̀san (ìyà), ẹ gbẹ̀san irú ìyà tí wọ́n fi jẹ yín. Dájúdájú tí ẹ bá sì ṣe sùúrù, òhun ló mà lóore jùlọ fún àwọn onísùúrù."
  17,91,"Tàbí kí o ní ọgbà oko dàbínù àti ọgbà oko àjàrà, tí o sì máa jẹ́ kí àwọn odò ṣàn kọ já dáadáa láààrin wọn."
  17,92,"Tàbí kí o jẹ́ kí sánmọ̀ já lù wá ní kélekèle gẹ́gẹ́ bí o ṣe sọ (pé Allāhu lè ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Tàbí kí o mú Allāhu àti àwọn mọlāika wá (bá wa) ní ojúkojú."
  17,93,"Tàbí kí o ní ilé wúrà kan, tàbí kí o gun òkè sánmọ̀ lọ. A kò sì níí gba gígun-sánmọ̀ rẹ gbọ́ títí o fi máa sọ tírà kan tí a óò máa ké kalẹ̀ fún wa.” Sọ pé: “Mímọ́ ni fún Olúwa mi, ǹjẹ́ mo jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe Òjíṣẹ́ abara?”"
  18,58,"Olúwa rẹ ni Aláforíjìn, Oníkẹ̀ẹ́. Bí ó bá jẹ́ pé Ó máa fi ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́ mú wọn ni, ìbá tètè mú ìyà wá fún wọn. Ṣùgbọ́n àkókò àdéhùn (àjíǹde) wà fún wọn. Wọn kò sì níí rí ibùsásí kan lẹ́yìn rẹ̀."
  18,59,"Ìwọ́nyí ni àwọn ìlú tí A ti parẹ́ nígbà tí wọ́n ṣàbòsí. A sì fún wọn ní (àkókò) àdéhùn fún ìparun wọn."
  18,60,"(Rántí) nígbà tí (Ànábì) Mūsā sọ fún ọmọ-ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀ pé: “Èmi kò níí yé rìn títí mo máa fi dé ibi tí odò méjì ti papọ̀ tàbí (títí) mo máa fi lo ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ọdún.”"
  19,19,"(Mọlāika) sọ pé: “Èmi ni Òjíṣẹ́ Olúwa rẹ, (Ó rán mi sí ọ) pé kí n̄g fún ọ ní ọmọkùnrin mímọ́ kan.”{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ànábì ‘Īsā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - àti gbogbo àwọn Ànábì ni ẹni mímọ́ gẹ́gẹ́ bí ó ṣe wà nínú āyah 13 nínú sūrah yìí kan náà pé ẹni mímọ́ ni Ànábì Yahyā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -.]
  19,20,"Ó sọ pé: “Báwo ni mo ṣe máa ní ọmọ nígbà tí abara kan kò fọwọ́ kàn mí, tí èmi kò sì jẹ́ alágbèrè.”"
  19,21,"(Mọlāika) sọ pé: “Báyẹn ló máa rí.” Olúwa rẹ sọ pé: “Ó rọrùn fún mi. Àti pé nítorí kí Á lè ṣe é ní àmì fún àwọn ènìyàn ni. Ó sì jẹ́ ìkẹ́ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Wa. Ó tún jẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ tí A ti parí (tí ó gbọ́dọ̀ wá sí ìmúṣẹ.)”"
  20,1,"Tọ̄ hā. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.){1}.",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  20,2,"A kò sọ al-Ƙur’ān kalẹ̀ fún ọ láti kó wàhálà bá ọ."
  20,3,"Bí kò ṣe pé ó jẹ́ ìrántí fún ẹni tó ń páyà (Allāhu)."